<p class="BubbleTitleSub">ARCIC Supports the Counter-WMD Mission</p>
<p>By COL Vance P. Visser, Chief, ARCIC, RID, Maneuver Support Protection Division, November 12, 2013</p>
<p>The existing threat to the United States posed by Weapons of Mass Destruction (WMD) is significant and growing.  At least 17 countries maintain sizeable chemical/biological weapons stockpiles and many, such as North Korea, possess amounts exceeding two metric tons.  The threat of conventional nuclear attack remains a national security concern.</p>
<div class="blockCallout" id="alignRt">
			<div class="blockimage"><asp:HyperLink runat="server"
